~ Root file ‚Äî pulls in every chapter via `reference` and renders the
~ assembled thesis. Order of `reference` lines determines chapter order.
~
~ Each chapter is invoked with an explicit close (`@chapter_one
~ chapter_one@`) ‚Äî block-form defs require it. Value-block defs
~ (#name: ‚Ä¶ !!) can be invoked bare from inside a paragraph but not
~ at top level cross-file, so block form is the right shape for
~ chapter exports.

reference ./chapters/01-introduction.wit
reference ./chapters/02-argument.wit

@h1 On Attention h1@

